Onboarding Request case
tw.local.newCaseProperties = new tw.object.Record();

// Client
tw.local.newCaseProperties.setPropertyValue("CO_ClientName", tw.local.client.name);

// Client Point of Contact
tw.local.newCaseProperties.setPropertyValue("CO_FirstName", tw.local.client.primaryContact.firstName);
tw.local.newCaseProperties.setPropertyValue("CO_LastName", tw.local.client.primaryContact.lastName);
tw.local.newCaseProperties.setPropertyValue("CO_Email", tw.local.client.primaryContact.email);
tw.local.newCaseProperties.setPropertyValue("CO_PhoneNumber", tw.local.client.primaryContact.phoneNumber);

// Client Address
tw.local.newCaseProperties.setPropertyValue("CO_AddressStreet", tw.local.client.address.street);
tw.local.newCaseProperties.setPropertyValue("CO_AddressUnit", tw.local.client.address.unit);
tw.local.newCaseProperties.setPropertyValue("CO_AddressCity", tw.local.client.address.city);
tw.local.newCaseProperties.setPropertyValue("CO_AddressState", tw.local.client.address.state);
tw.local.newCaseProperties.setPropertyValue("CO_AddressZipCode", tw.local.client.address.zipCode);
tw.local.newCaseProperties.setPropertyValue("CO_AddressCountry", tw.local.client.address.country);

// Client Additional Info
tw.local.newCaseProperties.setPropertyValue("CO_AnnualRevenue", tw.local.client.additionalInformation.annualRevenue);
tw.local.newCaseProperties.setPropertyValue("CO_CompanyAge", tw.local.client.additionalInformation.companyAge);
tw.local.newCaseProperties.setPropertyValue("CO_DefaultedPayment", tw.local.client.additionalInformation.defaultedPayment);
tw.local.newCaseProperties.setPropertyValue("CO_NumberOfEmployees", tw.local.client.additionalInformation.numberOfEmployees);

// Client Services
tw.local.newCaseProperties.setPropertyValue("CO_Industry", tw.local.industry);
tw.local.newCaseProperties.setPropertyValue("CO_ServicesFee", tw.local.servicesFee);
tw.local.newCaseProperties.setPropertyValue("CO_ServicesRequested", tw.local.servicesRequested);

// Reviewed Documents
var reviewedDocuments = tw.local.reviewedDocuments;
var caseReviewedDocuments = new tw.object.listOf.Record();
for(var i = 0; i < reviewedDocuments.listLength; i++) {
	caseReviewedDocuments[i] = new tw.object.Record();
	caseReviewedDocuments[i].setPropertyValue("CO_DocumentName", reviewedDocuments[i].documentName.toString());
	caseReviewedDocuments[i].setPropertyValue("CO_DocumentStatus", reviewedDocuments[i].documentStatus.toString());
}
tw.local.newCaseProperties.setPropertyValue("CO_ReviewedDocuments", caseReviewedDocuments);

// Selected Document IDs
if(!!tw.local.selectedDocumentIDs && tw.local.selectedDocumentIDs.listLength > 0) {
	tw.local.newCaseProperties.setPropertyValue("CO_SelectedDocumentIDs", tw.local.selectedDocumentIDs);
}

// Reference ID
tw.local.newCaseProperties.setPropertyValue("CO_ReferenceID", tw.local.referenceID);

// User ID
tw.local.newCaseProperties.setPropertyValue("CO_UserID", tw.local.userID);

// Create Case
tw.local.caseID = tw.system.currentProcessInstance.createCase("CO_ClientOnboardingRequest", tw.local.newCaseProperties, null, true);</ns15:script></ns15:scriptTask><ns15:sequenceFlow
